metadata.name: Cosa Monstra - [UNREVEALED]
metadata.description: COSA MONSTRA GENESIS is a collection of 1,322 unique NFTs on the Ethereum blockchain by GABOR CSUPO, co-creator of Rugrats, Aaahh!!! Real Monsters, The Wild Thornberrys, Rocket Power and many more childhood classics.Your COSA MONSTRA GENESIS doubles as an Inkhead Studios Membership Pass with perks, utility and benefits.Owners of COSA MONSTRA GENESIS have IP & commercial rights with their characters.
